Variable definitions

$description_full
Main content of issue

$description_short
Short description that summarizes issue/pull request

$linked_authors...
list of linked authors
format:
[github username](github user url)

$linked_mentions...
list of linked mentions to relevent people
format:
[github username](github user url)

$linked_self_reference
linked reference to issue/pull request
format:
[$uuid_short](url)

$uuid_full
prng 128 bits in 4 blocks of 8 hex characters

$uuid_short
first block of $uuid_full

$timestamp_full
ISO 8601 UTC timestamp. 24 hour time
format:
yyyy-MM-ddThh:mm:ssZ

$timestamp_short
date part of $timestamp_full
